"Bonny!"
cried
Mr.
Yorke.
"That's
the
reason
that
he
should
be,
and
proof
that
he
is,
a
scoundrel."
"But
he
looks
too
sorrowful
to
be
false,"
here
interposed
a
quiet
voice
from
behind
the
father's
